    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>COSMIC CALL</i></strong> is a <strong>brutal 3D FPS Roguelike Boomer shooter</strong> set inside the prison of the Great One. Many have entered this prison, succumbing to its never-ending torture and its relentless <strong>cycle of death</strong> and retries, but none have ever managed to escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>50+</strong> <strong>WEAPONS</strong> TO USE</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>100+</strong> <strong>POWERUPS</strong> TO FIND</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>150+</strong> <strong>ENEMIES</strong> TO DESTROY</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>30+</strong> <strong>BOSSES</strong> TO DEFEAT</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CHALLENGING GAMEPLAY</strong> / NO HANDHOLDING</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>REACTIVE WOLRD</strong> (CHAOS INCREASES BASED ON RUN-TIME)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DIVERSE WEAPONS &amp; ITEMS</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BREAK THE GAME</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PAINT THE WALLS RED</strong> IN <strong>VARIOUS AREAS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060130/extras/78220f7169bc2294d498af83e2d821a9.poster.avif?t=1770482640\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060130/extras/78220f7169bc2294d498af83e2d821a9.webm?t=1770482640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060130/extras/78220f7169bc2294d498af83e2d821a9.mp4?t=1770482640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FIGHT WITH <strong>POWERFUL OTHERWORDLY WEAPONS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060130/extras/80706f7ce9edadc556421fd4f78e3599.poster.avif?t=1770482640\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060130/extras/80706f7ce9edadc556421fd4f78e3599.webm?t=1770482640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060130/extras/80706f7ce9edadc556421fd4f78e3599.mp4?t=1770482640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BLOW</strong> YOUR <strong>ENEMIES </strong>TO <strong>BITS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060130/extras/c591b05bf357ee93fc20297142111f2d.poster.avif?t=1770482640\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060130/extras/c591b05bf357ee93fc20297142111f2d.webm?t=1770482640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060130/extras/c591b05bf357ee93fc20297142111f2d.mp4?t=1770482640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
